data.description: Location! Space! Detail! This house will spoil you. Pull up to this beautiful corner lot with side entry garage and take in the view. Gorgeous upgraded light fixtures greet you in both the foyer and the dining room. Custom wainscoting frames the walls in your spacious dining room. The office to your right offers privacy for work or an extra living space for the family. The kitchen, with it's custom herringbone pattern tile backsplash and gas oven range, faces the living room for an open concept plan. Utilize a custom built mud bench to store shoes or hang bags. You'll appreciate the privacy this split floor plan offers with it's Owner's suite on one side and 3 bedrooms on the other. This home has so much to offer. Hurry! It won't last!
